Package: mindy
Title: RStudio Bridge for Mindy CLI
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Mindy", , , "mindy@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Enables the Mindy CLI to execute R code in the current RStudio
    session. Uses a file-based communication mechanism where the CLI writes
    commands and R executes them via rstudioapi::sendToConsole().
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    later,
    uuid
Suggests:
    rstudioapi,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
